    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "comment-intro",
        "type": "nodetool.workflows.base_node.Comment",
        "data": {
          "comment": "# 🎯 Cold Outreach Co-Pilot\n\nName a prospect or company and an autonomous agent researches them on the web, then drafts a personalized cold email that opens with a real, specific detail.\n\n**Pipeline:** Prospect + your offer → build objective → Research agent (search + browse) → structured draft\n\nThe agent returns `subject`, `body`, and `follow_up` as separate typed fields (not one prose blob), so each piece can be previewed, edited, or piped into a CRM/email tool on its own.\n\n**Try this:** change the prospect, paste your real offer, or tell the agent the tone to use. Pick a model on the agent first."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "position": {
            "x": -540,
            "y": -262
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 480,
          "height": 240,
          "selectable": true,
          "bypassed": false
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {},
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "input_prospect",
        "type": "nodetool.input.StringInput",
        "data": {
          "name": "Prospect / Company",
          "description": "The person or company to research and reach out to.",
          "value": "AtlasCloud"
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "selected": false,
          "position": {
            "x": 50,
            "y": 403
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 280,
          "title": "1️⃣ Prospect",
          "selectable": true,
          "bypassed": false
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {},
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "input_offer",
        "type": "nodetool.input.StringInput",
        "data": {
          "name": "Your Offer",
          "description": "What you sell and the outcome it drives.",
          "value": "We build NodeTool - a Creative AI workspace."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "position": {
            "x": 50,
            "y": 649
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 280,
          "title": "2️⃣ Your offer",
          "selectable": true,
          "bypassed": false
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {},
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "objective",
        "type": "nodetool.text.Prompt",
        "data": {
          "prompt": "Research the prospect and draft outreach.\n\nPROSPECT:\n{{ prospect }}\n\nMY OFFER:\n{{ offer }}\n\nSteps:\n1. Use google_search and browser to learn what the prospect does, their stage, and anything recent (a launch, hire, funding, or post).\n2. Identify 2–4 pain points my offer plausibly solves for them.\n3. Write a cold email under 120 words that OPENS with a specific researched detail, ties it to one pain point, and ends with a low-friction ask.\n4. Write one short follow-up for no-reply, 3–5 days later.\n\nReturn JSON with these exact fields (subject and body as separate, structured fields — never combine them into one string):\n{\n  \"company_summary\": \"<2–3 sentences on what they do + recent signal>\",\n  \"pain_points\": [\"<pain 1>\", \"<pain 2>\", ...],\n  \"subject\": \"<email subject line, under 8 words, no clickbait>\",\n  \"body\": \"<email body only, no subject line inside it, under 120 words>\",\n  \"follow_up\": \"<short nudge, under 40 words>\"\n}"
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "position": {
            "x": 390,
            "y": 332
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 340,
          "height": 460,
          "title": "3️⃣ Build research objective",
          "selectable": true,
          "bypassed": false
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {
          "prospect": null,
          "offer": null
        },
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "agent",
        "type": "nodetool.agents.Agent",
        "data": {
          "model": {
            "type": "language_model",
            "id": "sonnet",
            "provider": "claude_agent_sdk",
            "name": "Claude Sonnet (subscription)"
          },
          "tools": [
            {
              "type": "tool_name",
              "name": "google_search"
            },
            {
              "type": "tool_name",
              "name": "browser"
            }
          ],
          "max_tokens": 100000,
          "system": "You are a B2B research assistant and senior cold-outreach copywriter.\n\nGoal\n- Research the given prospect/company using the tools, then draft outreach that references something specific and true about them.\n\nTools Available\n- google_search: Search the web for information\n- browser: Open URLs and read content\n\nWorkflow\n1. Search for the prospect/company; identify what they do and recent news.\n2. Browse their site or a recent post to find concrete, current details.\n3. Map their likely pain points to the offer.\n4. Draft a short, human, non-salesy email plus one follow-up.\n\nOutput Format\n- Return a single JSON object matching the defined output schema — `subject`, `body`, and `follow_up` are separate fields, never merged into one string.\n- The email body must open with a specific, researched detail (never \"I hope this finds you well\").\n- Keep the body under 120 words and the follow-up under 40. Cite sources where useful.\n",
          "mode": "loop"
        },
